Sentencas: Novel Sm2O3-NiO composite was prepared as the functional electrolyte for the first time.
Titulo: The composite electrolyte with an insulation Sm2O3 and semiconductor NiO for advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: The total electrical conductivity of Sm2O3-NiO is 0.38 S cm(-1) in H-2/air condition at 550 degrees C. High performance, e.g. 718 mW cm(-2), was achieved using Sm2O3-NiO composite as an electrolyte of solid oxide fuel cells operated at 550 degrees C.
Titulo: The composite electrolyte with an insulation Sm2O3 and semiconductor NiO for advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical properties and electrochemical performance are strongly depended on Sm2O3 and NiO constituent phase of the compositions.
Titulo: The composite electrolyte with an insulation Sm2O3 and semiconductor NiO for advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: Notably, surprisingly high ionic conductivity and fuel cell performance are achieved using the composite system constituting with insulating Sm2O3 and intrinsic p-type conductive NiO with a low conductivity of 4 x 10(-3) S cm(-1).
Titulo: The composite electrolyte with an insulation Sm2O3 and semiconductor NiO for advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: The interfacial ionic conduction between two phases is a dominating factor giving rise to significantly enhanced proton conduction.
Titulo: The composite electrolyte with an insulation Sm2O3 and semiconductor NiO for advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: Fuel cell performance and further ionic conduction mechanisms are under investigation.
Titulo: The composite electrolyte with an insulation Sm2O3 and semiconductor NiO for advanced fuel cells
